title: 3 BED 3 BATHS ** Wilson L Train ** NO FEE - W/D IN UNIT
posting_body: ['9/1 move in date', 'No broker fee', 'Text Lihi @ 3477484234 w/ address - 237 Covert St', 'Entire second floor of a 3 story / 3 unit Townhome!', '- Renovated modern 3 bedroom with 3 full baths and in unit washer dryer in Bushwick!', '- Located on Covert St between Irving Ave and Knickerbocker Ave, a very quiet, clean and residential area in trendy Bushwick right near the Irving Square Park, short walk to the L Train at Wilson Ave or Halsey stop, as well as the J train.', 'Bushwick has lots to offer, you can find some of the best restaurants, bars, and coffee shops within walking distance including Industry 1332, Father Knows Best, Houdini Kitchen Laboratory, Nowadays and more… Apartment is a full second floor of a 3 unit / 3 story Townhouse, spacious bedrooms with windows and closets, each with their own bathroom, central air and heat, video intercom system, hardwood flooring, in unit washer dryer, kitchen with island, pets allowed *upon approval, Guarantors Accepted, Showing by appointment, No brokers fee!']
